comment: McCallum (SAC) does not make contact with Asik's (NOP) arm.
Gordon (NOP) does not push off of McLemore (SAC) and affects his ability to defend.
Cunningham (NOP) does not dislodge Casspi (SAC) on the rebound attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Casspi (SAC) was the last player to touch the ball before it went OOB was upheld and NOP is awarded possession.
Casspi (SAC) legally contests Davis' (NOP) jump shot.
Asik (NOP) makes contact with Cousins' (SAC) head on the rebound attempt.
Casspi (SAC) grabs Davis' (NOP) arm and prevents him from sceuring the rebound.
Davis (NOP) sets the screen on McCallum (SAC) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Cousins (SAC) maintains legal guarding position defending the layup attempt by Evans (NOP).
Asik (NOP) does not affect Cousins' (SAC) RSBQ on the baseline drive.
McLemore (SAC) commits a take foul on Evans (NOP).
Gordon's (NOP) contact does not prevent McLemore (SAC) from freely moving.
The contact by Asik (NOP) does not affect Cousins' (SAC) ability to retrieve the rebound.
Asik (NOP) grabs Cousins (SAC) and restricts his ability to cleanly catch the inbounds pass.
Asik's (NOP) contact does not affect Cousins' (SAC) shot attempt.
McLemore (SAC) commits a take foul on Gordon (NOP).
McCallum (SAC) initiates contact with Evans (NOP) who maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket.
McCallum (SAC) jumps with the ball and returns to the floor without releasing it.
Stauskas (SAC) commits a take foul on Evans NOP).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that McCallum (SAC) was the last player to touch ball before it went OOB was overturned and SAC was awarded possession.
